text: For users integrating with Google, we collect and store links to your Google Meet transcript Google Doc files, then analyze these files with artificial intelligence to provide you with key insights.

data_type: link to meeting phone call transcript
text: For users integrating with Zoom, we collect and store links to your meeting/phone call transcripts, analyzing these to provide you with valuable insights regarding those meetings and associating these insights with your contacts in HubSpot based on the attendee email addresses for that meeting.
